Yes another Game of Thrones character. The first time I made him it was really awful, but this time I think he actually resembles the actor so I am releasing him seperately.
If anyone is interested I will try to make Daenerys next, so let me know!



This save is right after character creation, just drop it in your Saves folder.






If you would like to download Ned Stark go [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=972]here[/url]
